# Checklist

Prior to approving and merging this PR every reviewer must make sure that the following points are addressed.

- The REST APIs introduced in this PR are following the guidelines
- The architecture documents are updated
- The PR includes unit tests that cover the functionality introduced/modified in a broad enough way
- Code is ...
  - well designed
  - readable by others
  - doing what the author intended
  - no more complex than needed
  - not degrading system code health
  - commented with the why vs. what
  - appropriately tested
  - sufficiently documented

